14.2.
Governing Law.
Jurisdiction and Venue.
This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the State of California and the United States without regard to conflicts of laws provisions thereof, and without regard to the United Nations Convention on the International Sale of Goods.
 The jurisdiction and venue for actions related to the subject matter hereof shall be the state and federal courts located in San Francisco, California and both parties hereby submit to the personal jurisdiction of such courts.
